-	Domain ID: A valid domain ID.
+	Domain ID: A valid domain ID. When writing, '*' applies the changes
+		   to all the domains.
 
 	Assignment states:
 
@@ -540,6 +541,35 @@ When monitoring is enabled all MON groups may also contain:
 	   mbm_total_bytes:0=e;1=e
