From 5303afbf203db02ef929d00997d9df4decb646fc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Myron Stowe <mstowe@redhat.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Apr 2026 09:04:53 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 210/482] PCI/pwrctrl: Skip scanning for the device further if
