From cd8149a4a0c88020899f5002bcd894fb8bbe21df Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Myron Stowe <mstowe@redhat.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:04:22 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 225/482] PCI: vmd: Switch to pci_bus_find_emul_domain_nr()

JIRA: https://issues.redhat.com/browse/RHEL-139975
Upstream Status: b37b6095a94e1ccecac80c9f1a8fca8d72919c65

